{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":102,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":null,"text":"高陵君叛乱造反，寡人立即亲自出战，尔等各人留在原席，待寡人收拾乱贼后，再来和各位卿家喝酒。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":164,"line_start":2,"line_end":2},{"speaker":"char_zhu_ji","speaker_name":"朱姬","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"王儿！这是什么一回事？","tone":"颤声","chapter":164,"line_start":8,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_zhu_ji","text":"太后放心，一切有王儿处理，人来！先扶太后回营休息。","tone":"淡然","chapter":164,"line_start":12,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"仲父和三小姐受惊了，请到寡人帐内小休片刻，乱事敉平后，寡人再请仲父出来喝杯祝捷酒。","tone":"陈述","chapter":164,"line_start":18,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_jing_shan","speaker_name":"荆善","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"给鲁残溜掉，由他接应的人均是来自外地，非吕不韦在咸阳的家将。","tone":"陈述","chapter":164,"line_start":68,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_zhu_ji","speaker_name":"朱姬","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"王儿看着办吧！","tone":"无奈","chapter":164,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_gao_ling_jun","text":"叛上造反，阴谋不轨，高陵君你可知罪？","tone":"淡然","chapter":164,"line_start":86,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_gao_ling_jun","speaker_name":"高陵君","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"呸！你这野种何来……","tone":"愤怒","chapter":164,"line_start":90,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"犯上造反，仲父以为该治以何罪？","tone":"陈述","chapter":164,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"自是罪该万死，储君先把他收入监牢，再昭告天下，择期行刑。","tone":"陈述","chapter":164,"line_start":96,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"仲父所言甚是，不过何须择日行刑，给我把他们全部推到泾水旁立即斩首，死后不得安葬，任由尸身曝于荒野，以佐猛兽之腹。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":164,"line_start":100,"line_end":102}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiao_pan","name":"小盘","alias":["嬴政","秦始皇"],"identity":"秦国储君，