ne_start":78,"line_end":78,"text":"遭捆绑的高陵君和十多个将领被推到场心"}]},{"id":"char_xiang_shao_long","name":"项少龙","alias":["项统领"],"identity":"秦国都骑军统领","faction":"faction_qin_guo","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"秦国都骑军统领，策划平定高陵君叛乱，被派离京彻查叛党接应之人","personality":{"traits":["机智","沉稳","仁厚","果断","重情义","淡泊名利"],"speech_style":"言辞简洁，不喜张扬","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"师徒","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"亦师亦父"},{"target":"char_ji_yan_ran","type":"恋人","intensity":80,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"爱侣"},{"target":"char_qin_qing","type":"恋人","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"互有好感"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[164],"source_refs":[{"chapter":164,"line_start":54,"line_end":54,"text":"项少龙自领两千都骑军，沿河搜索"}]},{"id":"char_jing_shan","name":"荆善","alias":[],"identity":"项少龙的部下","faction":"faction_qin_guo","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"初窥门径","one_line":"项少龙部下，报告鲁残逃脱的消息","personality":{"traits":["忠诚","勤快","机敏","服从","务实"],"speech_style":"报告式","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"主仆","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"忠心部下"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[164],"source_refs":[{"chapter":164,"line_start":68,"line_end":68,"text":"荆善又来报告道"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_qin_guo","name":"秦国","type":"武林门派","location":"咸阳","sub_divisions":["禁卫军","都骑军","都卫军"],"one_line":"战国七雄之一，小盘为储君，吕不韦为仲父","source_refs":[{"chapter":164,"line_start":2,"line_end":2,"text":"小盘在徐先、鹿公、王陵三名大将陪同下"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_guan_zhong_xie","updates":{},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"对手","intensity":60,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"首次感受到与项少龙对敌的可怕感觉"}]}]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":103,"line_end":198,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":null,"text":"凡与乱党有关的家属，男的发往西疆开荒，女的充为官婢，高陵君子子孙孙全体处死，凡有异心者，均以此为戒。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":164,"line_start":112,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":null,"text":"今趟功劳最大者，是刚加入都骑军的桓齮，全赖他先一步识破叛党的阴谋，寡人才得以从容部署，将贼子一网成擒，应记首功。寡人把他破格升为将军，而王翦荐人有功，兼之在北疆战绩彪炳，擢升为大将军，立时生效。","tone":"陈述","chapter":164,"line_start":124,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":null,"text":"桓齮将军将留守京师，成立训练营，专责训练由各地精选送来的新兵，提拔人才，为我大秦将来一统天下打好根基。王贲今趟勇猛杀敌，斩敌首二十，立下大功，寡人任他为桓将军副将，同为我大秦出力。太后、仲父、上将军、大将军和众卿家可有异议？","tone":"陈述","chapter":164,"line_start":142,"line_end":146},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_zhu_ji","text":"太后！孩儿在听你的指示。","tone":"陈述","chapter":164,"line_start":152,"line_end":152},{"speaker":"char_zhu_ji","speaker_name":"朱姬","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"王儿自己拿主意好了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":164,"line_start":154,"line_end":154},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"禁卫、都骑、都卫三军，有足够实力作京城防卫的支柱，是否还需要另立新军？请储君明察。","tone":"陈述","chapter":164,"line_start":156,"line_end":158},{"speaker":"char_lu_gong","speaker_name":"鹿公","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"仲父正说出问题所在，禁卫、都骑和都卫若只论守城，实力绰有余裕，但若以之平定京城以外的动乱，却力有不逮，像今趟为了平东郡之乱，把京城附近的驻军全抽空了，令高陵君有可乘之机，故此新军实有成立之必要。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":164,"line_start":160,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_xu_xian","speaker_name":"徐先","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"现时我大秦与三晋势成水火，说不定要同时在几条战线与敌周旋，有了这支精锐的新军，就不怕再有像东郡那种动乱和民变了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":164,"line_start":164,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"这事就依此安排，项统领接令。","tone":"严肃","chapter":164,"line_start":172,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"高陵君能以万人之众，神不知鬼不觉地潜来京城，途中必有接应之人，寡人要项统领立即离京，彻查此事，若发觉有任何人曾为叛党出力，立杀无赦，统领在京的职务暂由荆副统领代行。","tone":"严肃","chapter":164,"line_start":180,"line_end":182},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":null,"text":"今晚宴会到此而止，诸卿先休息一会儿，待桥修好后，再和寡人到泾水迎接晚猎回来的大队人马，检阅他们的丰富收获。","tone":"陈述","chapter":164,"line_start":186,"line_end":188}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_chang_ping_jun","name":"昌平君","alias":[],"identity":"秦国贵族","faction":"faction_qin_guo","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"秦国贵族，率领禁卫军擒杀叛党，押送高陵君行刑","personality":{"traits":["忠诚","果断","勇猛","服从","正直"],"speech_style":"命令式","temperament":"刚毅"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"忠心辅佐"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[164],"source_refs":[{"chapter":164,"line_start":40,"line_end":40,"text":"昌平君兄弟便率领伏在两旁的五千禁卫军杀进高陵君的营地"}]},{"id":"char_lu_gong","name":"鹿公","alias":[],"identity":"秦国大将","faction":"faction_qin_guo","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"秦国大将，支持小盘，力主成立新军","personality":{"traits":["豪迈","直率","忠诚","老练","威严"],"speech_style":"呵呵笑道，言辞直率","temperament":"豪爽"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"忠心支持"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[164],"source_refs":[{"chapter":164,"line_start":2,"line_end":2,"text":"小盘在徐先、鹿公、王陵三名大将陪同下"}]},{"id":"char_xu_xian","name":"徐先","alias":[],"identity":"秦国大将","faction":"faction_qin_guo","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"秦国大将，支持成立新军以应对多线作战","personality":{"traits":["沉稳","老练","忠诚","谨慎","有远见"],"speech_style":"言辞稳重","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"忠心支持"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[164],"source_refs":[{"chapter":164,"line_start":2,"line_end":2,"text":"小盘在徐先、鹿公、王陵三名大将陪同下"}]},{"id":"char_wang_ling","name":"王陵","alias":[],"identity":"秦国大将","faction":"faction_qin_guo","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"秦国大将，陪同小盘回场","personality":{"trait